Author: XcelR
Title: [ANN]XcelR-Changing the way cryptocurrecny is exchanged [PoW][Bounty][Platform]
Body: Please follow the directions in the main thread, on how to set your wallet up in legacy mode. Make sure you back up your original wallet.dat then delete the wallets folder in your .xcelr folder. Then Restart your client and you should be able to Send and receive transactions without any problems. You will have to push the transactions through yourself to your wallet.

Author: XcelR
Title: [ANN]XcelR-Changing the way cryptocurrecny is exchanged [PoW][Bounty][Platform]
Body: All our wallets are safe, We are implementing more security protocols for our applications in the coming weeks!

Author: XcelR
Title: [ANN]XcelR-Changing the way cryptocurrecny is exchanged [PoW][Bounty][Platform]
Body: Please run the following command  xcelrd -zapwallettxes -addresstype=legacy --printtoconsole  xcelr-cli stop  wait for the server to stop  then run xcelrd -rescan -addresstype=legacy --daemon  when it's finished scanning run this command  xcelr-cli -getinfo and it will show you your balance.  Please email our support team if you have any more questions  support@xcelr.org

Author: XcelR
Title: [ANN]XcelR-Changing the way cryptocurrecny is exchanged [PoW][Bounty][Platform]
Body: XcelR Is Getting A Reboot Stay Tuned!       XcelR  Changing the way cryptocurrecny is exchanged, purchased and used around the world!  https://i.imgur.com/AJiDjEi.png  https://i.imgur.com/NIWD1zW.png  https://i.imgur.com/TrHukZU.png  https://i.imgur.com/60QrBVM.png  https://i.imgur.com/9Fi5mz4.png  https://i.imgur.com/Z1WfZhz.png  https://i.imgur.com/F77lP58.png  https://i.imgur.com/8CxjEzO.png  https://i.imgur.com/XltJmIH.png    Existing exchanges offer access to just one source of trading, our platform offers over 12+ exchanges you can trade on from one place. This streamline the users experience and enables them to have efficient and effective trading campaigns. The platform will includes an array of features including easy cryptocurrency payment integration, digital arbitration systems, 10+ trading indicators & much more.  At the end, Our aim is to help businesses, Companies and everyday people purchase cryptocurrency more fluidly and efficiently with little to no friction this will help make business truly efficient, transparent, and reliable.    Block Explorer https://i.imgur.com/nc4jPmb.png   XcelR Apps  You will be able to access the XcelR Platform right from your devices Web Browser everything is optimized to provide the user with a frictionless experience. We also offer a Mobile Wallet App for both Android and iPhone devices. You will be able to download these wallets on the Google Play Store and the Apple App Store. Some of the features are listed below.  XcelR Platform Updates  https://i.imgur.com/JJ6m7Yc.png https://i.imgur.com/dTjVSji.png https://i.imgur.com/u1OxtVl.png https://i.imgur.com/RRm2N6v.png  Fully Optimized Market Platform Secure and Frictionless Wallet Integration High Speed Network Low to No transaction fees  XcelR Promo Video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKyG8dpDVSk   XcelR Founder Linkedin Profile  https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottkaleita/   XcelR Roadmap  March 2018 - Start of the XcelR Platform Development. April 2018 - Start of XcelR Coin Development. June 2018 - Completion of XcelR Coin. July 2018 - Start of XcelR Premine 1,008,000 Coins. August 2018 - Exchange Listings September 2018 - Partnershipsl January 2019 - Cryptocurrency Kiosk Roll Out April 2019 - XcelR Platform Updates May 2019 - TBA Partnerships July 2019 - XcelR Gets a Reboot   Partnerships https://xcelr.org/images/safeledger.png We are now partnered with Safe Ledger - Store your coins securely with the Safe Ledger Today! - Get 10% off when you purchase a Safe Ledger using this link - https://www.safeledger.tech/discount/XcelR   Exchanges  VaultMeX https://xcelr.org/images/vaultmex.png   XcelR is now Listed on VaultMeX - https://www.vaultmex.com/trade/XCL/BTC   Start-Ex Exchange https://i.imgur.com/W9JDXpy.png  XcelR is now Listed on Start-Ex Exchange - https://start-ex.com/trade/XCL_BTC     Exchange Voting  You can Vote For XcelR To Get Listed on Aiodex here - https://aiodex.com/vote/coin/5b65258aa315090673cbb74f#     XcelR Web Wallet  https://i.imgur.com/nchb7Ml.png Our Web Wallet is now Live and you can Sign Up and Send/Receive Coins  The Official Wallet Address is https://xcelrwallet.online  You can also find the Official Link on our Website https://xcelr.org   XcelR Official IRC Server  Join us on our Official IRC Server Here: 149.255.32.141:6667  Join the XcelR Channel By typing /join #XcelR  WebsiteÔªø | WhitepaperÔªø | Block ExplorerÔªø | PlatformÔªø | GithubÔªø | TwitterÔªø | FacebookÔªø | TelegramÔªø | MediumÔªø | Reddit | Discord   XcelR Masternodes  By Default Our DNS Seeder will pick up all the active nodes on the network. If by chance the DNS Seeder is not working you can add these into you xcelr.conf file.  addnode=149.255.32.153:4458 addnode=138.201.45.124:4458 addnode=67.183.127.97:4458   XcelR Conf File Please Make Sure Your Conf File Looks Like This Code: addnode=138.201.45.111:4458 addnode=149.255.32.168:4458 addnode=107.150.28.160:4458 addnode=149.255.32.155:4458 addnode=149.255.32.153:4458 addnode=138.201.45.124:4458 addnode=67.183.127.97:4458 listen=1 walletbroadcast=1 addresstype=legacy  Run a XcelR Masternode If you would like to run a XcelR Node you can purchase a VPS here they range from $4-$7 https://vps.cool/  Once you have purchase a VPS Make Sure your OS is Ubuntu 14.04/16.04 and install the XcelR Dependencies You can find out more on how to install the xcelr dependencies on our github here https://github.com/xcelr/XcelR  Once you have install the Dependencies you can download our repo to the VPS by installing Git apt install git  Then Run: git clone https://github.com/xcelr/XcelR  Then run the following commands: cd XcelR ./autogen.sh ./configure make make install  Once Fully Installed Run:  xcelrd -addresstype=legacy --daemon  or  xcelrd -addresstype=legacy --printtoconsole to see if the node is running correctly    Mine XcelR on Minpool.net Code: -a scrypt -o stratum+tcp://minpool.net:6900 -u your_wallet_address -p c=XCL   Mine XcelR is now on TeraPool Code: -a scrypt -o stratum+tcp://pool.tera.tn:3433  -u  <WALLET>  -p c=XCL   Mine XcelR on PowerPool.money Code: ccminer -a scrypt -o stratum+tcp://powerpool.money:3433 -u <XCL_WALLET_ADDRESS> -p "WorkerName c=XCL"   XcelR Bounties  Join The Telegram Group = 5 XCL Like the Facebook Page = 5 XCL Follow Us On Twitter = 5 XCL Sign up on the XcelR Platform = 15 XCL  View The Full List Of Bounties Here https://xcelr.org/bounty.pdf    Translations  Russian Translation: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4772427   (Thanks to anstarnet) Hindi Translation: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4776664.0   (Thanks to desi_translator2018)   Update: XcelR Update v16.2 is now on Guthub @ https://github.com/xcelr/XcelR  Update: Our Block Explorer is now back up with a whole new design. Check it out! https://explorer.xcelr.org   _______________________________________________________________________________ __________________________  The XcelR CEL Air Gapped Wallet  Below are some Prototype pictures of the XcelR CEL Air Gapped Wallet. You will be able to use the XcelR CEL wallet with our platform and our Cryptocurrency Kiosks when we roll them out.   XcelR CEL Wallet Prototype V1   https://i.imgur.com/u27d9Yl.jpg   Prototype V1 is a basic model with a Andrino nano & OLED Screen. (Some parts are missing in this picture as it is just a mockup prototype. The Missing parts are - nrf24l01+ Wireless Transceiver Module - & A Tactile Button)   XcelR CEL Wallet Prototype V2   https://i.imgur.com/Njdzs7D.jpg   Prototype V2 has a Fully Responsive Touch Screen Built over a Andrino Leonardo - Touch Screen is 2-1/2 in. We will cut the thickness down to about 1-1/2 cm
